alMechanics/CanonicalEnsemble/Basic.html#CanonicalEnsemble.dof\">dof</a></span></span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Analysis/SpecialFunctions/Log/Basic.html#Real.log\">Real.log</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">𝓒</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/StatisticalMechanics/CanonicalEnsemble/Basic.html#CanonicalEnsemble.phaseSpaceunit\">phaseSpaceunit</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Fundamental relation between thermodynamic and differential entropy:\n`S_thermo = S_diff - kB * dof * log h`. ","docLink":"./PhysLean/StatisticalMechanics/CanonicalEnsemble/Lemmas.html#CanonicalEnsemble.thermodynamicEntropy_eq_differentialEntropy_sub_correction","kind":"theorem","line":135,"name":"CanonicalEnsemble.thermodynamicEntropy_eq_differentialEntropy_sub_correction","sourceLink":"https://github.com/HEPLean/PhysLean#L135-L199"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">theorem</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./PhysLean/StatisticalMechanics/CanonicalEnsemble/Lemmas.html#CanonicalEnsemble.kB_mul_beta\"><span class=\"name\">CanonicalEnsemble</span>.<span class=\"name\">kB_mul_beta</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">T</span> : <a href=\"./PhysLean/Thermodynamics/Temperature/Basic.html#Temperature\">Temperature</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">hT</span> : <span class=\"fn\">0</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#LT.lt\">&lt;</a> <span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T</span>.<a href=\"./PhysLean/Thermodynamics/Temperature/Basic.html#Temperature.val\">val</a></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./PhysLean/StatisticalMechanics/BoltzmannConstant.html#Constants.kB\">Constants.kB</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#HMul.hMul\">*</a> <span class=\"fn\">↑<span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">T</span>.<a href=\"./Ph